-- Jon Corzine Can’t Pay Damages With Creditor Money: U.S.
-- B y   T i f f a n y   K a r y
-- 2013-11-01T14:34:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-01/jon-corzine-can-t-pay-damages-with-creditor-money-u-s-.html
Jon Corzine , the former head of MF
Global Holdings Ltd., shouldn’t be able to use money that would
flow to creditors of the bankrupt futures broker to cover the
damages he and others caused to its former customers, according
to a court filing today from the Commodity Futures Trading
Commission.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tiffany Kary in New York at 
